page.title: 03An average Wednesday part 2
page.content: have their lunch.When I finished eating my sandwiches we practised majorettes for the fete. In the afternoon we did our project. My project is on music.Later we played rounders with the 3rd years. When I got home from school I watched T.V. until my dinner was ready.For dinner I had chips,beans,and a beefburger. After dinner I went out to play. When I came in I had my bath and went down to watch Dallas.Dallas is my favourite T.V. programme.I like it because there are good characters in it.Also the B.B.C think it out very carefully.When Dallas had finished I read my books for a little while then went to sleep.
